@node english "The first official icon collection for TWILIGHT"

   Did you ever remarked how sad is your Workbench ?!. It is true that there are many
solutions as Magic Workbench or NewIcon but its is greyish with Magic Workbench and I don't
think that NewIcon is good looking. That's why some people worked on the problem
and found a solution. This solution is called @{"TWILIGHT" Link Twilight2}. You can ask for informations
to @{"MELINA SOFTWORKS" LINK Mťlina2}. Now we can have a beautiful Workbench in 256 colors so I decided
to work and create some icons for the TWILIGHT system.

One of the problems was the size of the icons that are all different from the others so I decided
to create a standard.

Each icon posses a @{"type" system "visage Images/Types"}.

The different types are:

      @{" The Applications" system "visage images/Applications"}
      @{" The Preferences " system "visage images/prefs"}
      @{" The Tools       " system "visage images/Tools"}
      @{" The Devices     " system "visage Images/devices"}
      @{" The Others      " system "visage Images/Autres"}
      @{" The Games       " system "visage Images/Games"}
      @{" The Drawers     " system "visage Images/Tiroirs"}
@endnode

