@node "Twilight2

TWILIGHT is a software pack adding many features to the Workbench and having a good
looking interface in 256 colors and believe me, it works very well.

The last version is the 1.1 but TWILIGHT is evolving every time in order to become
the best in Workbench enhancement.
@endnode
